\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Measured angular frequencies for the three characteristic vibrational modes of the coupled oscillator system. The currently populated values represent the FFT analysis, alongside placeholders for the fitting parameters. The uncertainty is the sample standard deviation of the repeated measurements.}}{3}{}%
